  <brief_title>Application of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning in Patients Undergoing Open Heart Surgeries</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Remote Preconditioning on Heart Resistance to Ischemia and Reperfusion Injury</official_title>
